author: philip
msg: Only single statements in wc-queries.sql are executed via
a semi-colon is ignored.  That means that some statements
setting up indices were not getting executed, and one statement
lost part of it selection criteria.
Remove most semi-colons to discourage multiple statements.
Remove semi-colons from ends of statements, convert statements that
were not getting executed into comments.
(STMT_UPDATE_COPYFROM): Remove semi-colon from middle of statement.
